'''2016年贊比亞大選'''於8月11日舉行，選出新一屆[[赞比亚总统列表|總統]]和[[赞比亚国民议会|赞比亚国民议会]]議員。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-30891239 Zambia votes in presidential elections] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-30891239 |date=20161118132809 }} BBC News, 20 January 2015</ref><ref>[http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/01/zambia-sets-presidential-election-august-2016-160104090148204.html Zambia sets presidential election to August 2016] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/01/zambia-sets-presidential-election-august-2016-160104090148204.html |date=20160823094311 }} Al Jazeera, 4 January 2016</ref>同時舉行對憲法修訂的[[公民投票|公民投票]]。<ref>[https://www.lusakatimes.com/2015/03/16/government-to-hold-referendum-along-side-the-2016-general-elections/ Government to hold Referendum along side the 2016 General Elections] {{Wayback|url=https://www.lusakatimes.com/2015/03/16/government-to-hold-referendum-along-side-the-2016-general-elections/ |date=20150408202854 }} Lusaka Times, 16 March 2015</ref>

贊比亞選舉委員會於2016年8月15日宣佈總統選舉最終結果，現任總統[[埃德加·倫古|埃德加·倫古]]取得186萬多票，以50.35%得票率成功連任，而主要對手[[國家發展聯合黨|國家發展聯合黨]]參選人[[哈卡因德·希奇萊馬|哈卡因德·希奇萊馬]]則取得176萬多票。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://world.gmw.cn/newspaper/2016-08/18/content_115356879.htm|title=埃德加·伦古连任赞比亚总统|work=光明網|date=2016-08-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160819014719/http://world.gmw.cn/newspaper/2016-08/18/content_115356879.htm|archivedate=2016-08-19|accessdate=2016-08-19}}</ref>

